title: Dmitri Tsypchenko
text:
Dmitri Olegovich Tsypchenko (; born 29 June 1999) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays as a <a href="centre%20forward">centre forward</a> for <a href="PFC%20Krylia%20Sovetov%20Samara">PFC Krylia Sovetov Samara</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Professional%20Football%20League">Russian Professional Football League</a> for <a href="FC%20Chertanovo%20Moscow">FC Chertanovo Moscow</a> on 29 July 2016 in a game against <a href="FC%20Kaluga">FC Kaluga</a>. He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for Chertanovo on 17 July 2018 in a game against <a href="FC%20Rotor%20Volgograd">FC Rotor Volgograd</a>.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> debut for <a href="PFC%20Krylia%20Sovetov%20Samara">PFC Krylia Sovetov Samara</a> on 30 July 2021 in a game against <a href="FC%20Spartak%20Moscow">FC Spartak Moscow</a>.
